project_descr: Preparation of participation of the Republic of Belarus in the United Nations Conference on Sustainable Development RIO+20

outputs.output_descr:
The project is aimed to assist  the Republic of Belarus in preparation for participation in RIO+20 United Nations Conference on Sustainable Development RIO+20, which will take place on 20 - 22 June 2012.
CPD outcome is 3.2: Sustainable use of the country's natural resources promoted
